revision.text: <noinclude> {{note|This page describes the flags defined in the {{c|EDebugLevel}} enum. It's mainly meant to be included into other pages that describe functions that use print levels, such as {{struct|Console}}, using the '''<nowiki>{{: EDebugLevel}}</nowiki>''' syntax. (This note will not be included.)}} </noinclude>:*'''{{c|DMSG_OFF}}''' — Print even developer messages are turned off. :*'''{{c|DMSG_ERROR}}''' — Print if the game is printing only error messages (developer = 1) :*'''{{c|DMSG_WARNING}}''' — Print if the game is printing warnings and higher (developer = 2) :*'''{{c|DMSG_NOTIFY}}''' — Print if the game is printing notifications and higher (developer = 3) :*'''{{c|DMSG_SPAMMY}}''' — Print if the game is printing any and all debug messages (developer = 4)<noinclude>[[Category:Include templates]]</noinclude>
